      "*COLLECTION OF CERTIFIED DUBSTEP CLASSICS - MOST HAVE NEVER BEEN
      AVAILABLE ON CD BEFORE* I love dubstep, you love dubstep, we love dubstep,
      don't we? So do Youngsta and Geeneus, two of Rinse FM's longest serving
      DJs and compilers of this here definitive selection of the last 5 years of
      the scene's developments. Youngsta steps to the decks first with a
      trademark flawless blend running from Tempa classic 'Sholay' from High
      Plains Drifter vs Goldspot Productions, to D1's 'Give it Back' covering
      certified nuggets from Skream, Caspa, Loefah, Benga, Skream, Headhunter,
      Skream, and Pinch, with a couple of Skream tracks dropped for guaranteed
      party good times. Geeneus' CD takes a trip into the darker end of the
      spectrum, starting with Shackleton's 'Blood on My Hands' and plumbing the
      depths of the style with loaded techy anthems from DMZ, The Bug, 2562, DJ
      Abstract, TRG and Burial amongst many others. You really can't fall off
      with this set, 2 CDs of absolute classics mixed to perfection by arguably
      two of the finest DJs in the pot..."
